Summary: round object, pale green in color
divs: Sighting DetailsMy brother and I were traveling north on Canal Road in the afternoon, bright sunshine and no wind. The windows were down in the vehical we were traveling in, as there was no AC in vehical, the object appeared from are right traveling west. It was moving at a high rate of speed. The object had no decernible markings and absolutely no sound whatever. The object disappeard because of trees blocking are view. Both my brother and I were astounded by the speed it was traveling. What made us notice the object in the first place was the britness of the object during the daylight. This object was not a jet plane or any other man made object. Our feelings at the time was we witnessed a UFO.
